==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Biped
<hw>Bi"ped</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having two feet;
two-footed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>By which the man, when heavenly life was ceased,⟦br⟧
Became a helpless, naked, <qex>biped</qex> beast.</q>
<rj><qau>Byrom.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

